  // ── Per-record wizard registry ────────────────────────────────
  //
  // Each entry carries ``render(host, recordHex, recordSize, applyFn)``
  // — the same shape as the transparent wizards but per-record.
  // ``applyFn(newHex)`` round-trips the bytes through
  // ``saip.update_record_bytes``.

  // 3GPP TS 31.102 §4.4.2.3 — Dialling Number / Short String record.
  // Used by EF.MSISDN, EF.ADN, EF.FDN, EF.SDN, EF.BDN. Record layout:
  //   [α B alpha]                    α = record_size - 14
  //   [1 B BCDLen]                  count of TON/NPI + BCD bytes used
  //   [1 B TON/NPI]                 b8=1, b7..b5 TON, b4..b1 NPI
