  // 3GPP TS 31.102 §4.2.66 — EF.SPDI (Service Provider Display
  // Information). BER-TLV transparent EF wrapping a PLMN list:
  //   A3 LL                                  outer SPDI tag
  //     80 LL                                  PLMN list tag
